        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".counter-container": {
              "ol": {
                "margin-bottom": "0",
                "li": {
                  "margin-bottom": "1rem"
                },
                "& when (@stylizedCounters)": {
                  "counter-reset": "myCounter",
                  "li": {
                    "list-style": "none",
                    "padding-left": "1rem",
                    "position": "relative",
                    "&:before": {
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "left": "-40px",
                      "margin-top": "5px",
                      "counter-increment": "myCounter",
                      "content": "counter(myCounter)",
                      "line-height": "40px",
                      "transition": "all .2s",
                      "color": "contrast(@iconColor)",
                      "background": "@iconColor",
                      "width": "40px",
                      "height": "40px",
                      "border-radius": "50%",
                      "display": "flex",
                      "align-items": "center",
                      "justify-content": "center",
                      "& when (@squareCounters)": {
                        "border-radius": "0"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "_name": "content9",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content9\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Stylized Counters\" name=\"stylizedCounters\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Square Counters\" name=\"squareCounters\" condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#1f6463\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"counter-container col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">While the claims made by the Quantum Millionaire program may seem incredible at first glance, a closer examination reveals the potential underlying truths. The program's foundation lies in the understanding that our perception of life often shapes our reality. By shifting from self-limiting beliefs such as \"I am always going to stay broke\" or \"nothing good ever comes to me,\" Quantum Millionaire encourages individuals to alter their narratives. The \"Two Cups Quantum Leap\" method proposes that one's aura and energy can attract and retain positive circumstances.\n<div>\n</div><div>Here are some of the remarkable benefits this manifestation method asserts:</div></h4>\n                <div class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                    <ol>\n                        <li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Tesla-Inspired Coil Technology : </b>At the heart of the system is a specially designed bifilar pancake coil based on Nikola Tesla’s original concepts. The blueprint provides detailed guidance on coil winding patterns, spacing, and electrical connections to help ensure accurate construction and optimal performance.<br></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Energy Collection &amp; Conversion :</b>&nbsp;The system utilizes electromagnetic principles to generate and manage electrical energy. Once activated, the generated power can be stored in compatible battery systems or converted through an inverter for use with standard household appliances</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Smart Power Management :</b>&nbsp;Integrated components such as capacitors, diodes, and control modules help regulate energy flow and improve system stability. Optional upgrades including monitoring meters, charge controllers, and automated switches provide greater control and efficiency.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Modular &amp; Expandable Design : </b>One of the system’s key advantages is its modular architecture. Additional power modules can be added over time, allowing users to scale their setup without rebuilding the entire system. This flexibility makes it suitable for homes, cabins, workshops, and recreational vehicles.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Resonance Optimization :</b> 7 Lazy Millionaire Habits :&nbsp;</span>Learn simple, smart habits that millionaires use to grow wealth with less effort. Ideal for anyone who wants to work smarter instead of harder.</li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Energy Storage &amp; Stability :</b>&nbsp;Capacitive storage components help smooth electrical output and reduce fluctuations. This contributes to a more stable power supply while helping protect connected devices from voltage irregularities.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Thermal Management :</b>&nbsp;Carefully selected materials and structural design considerations help support reliable operation during extended usage by assisting with heat dissipation and system stability.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Safety Features</b> : The Energy Revolution System includes comprehensive safety guidelines covering voltage testing, polarity verification, grounding procedures, and protective fusing. These measures are designed to promote safe installation and operation.&nbsp;</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Hybrid Compatibility</b> : For users seeking greater flexibility, the system can be integrated with existing battery banks, backup power solutions, or renewable energy setups. This allows the creation of a customized energy system tailored to individual needs.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Complete Step-By-Step</b> : Blueprint From initial component preparation to final testing, every stage of the process is explained in clear detail. The comprehensive guide focuses on simplicity, accuracy, and long-term usability, helping users confidently build and expand their own energy system.</span></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li>\n                    </ol>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
