          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    Enter your subtitle here\n                </h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>&nbsp;The Energy Revolution System?</b><br><br><b>Michael Garnett</b> is the creator of the <b>Energy Revolution System</b>. As an inventor, independent energy researcher, and lifelong enthusiast of alternative energy technologies, he has spent years studying <b>Tesla-inspired energy</b> concepts and practical methods for achieving energy independence.<br><br>Driven by a passion for innovation and a desire to help homeowners reduce rising electricity costs, <b>Michael focused</b> his research on electromagnetic induction, resonance optimization, and bifilar coil technology. His goal was to create a simple, affordable system that ordinary people could build without requiring advanced technical knowledge or expensive equipment.<br><br>The result is the <b>Energy Revolution System</b> — a step-by-step blueprint designed to help users understand renewable energy principles and explore Tesla-inspired power generation concepts using easy-to-source materials and straightforward instructions.<br><br><b>Michael’s vision</b> is based on accessibility, simplicity, and self-reliance. By combining classic electrical theories with modern energy management techniques, he has created a practical learning system that makes alternative energy technology easier to understand and implement.<br><br><b>Mission :&nbsp;</b>To help households achieve greater energy independence through affordable, scalable, and easy-to-follow energy solutions that reduce reliance on traditional power sources.<br><br><b>Approach :&nbsp;</b>The Energy Revolution System simplifies complex electromagnetic concepts into clear instructions, diagrams, and implementation steps, allowing users to build and expand their own energy projects with confidence.<br><br><b>Support :&nbsp;</b>Every Energy Revolution System purchase includes lifetime blueprint updates and dedicated customer support, helping users learn, build, test, and optimize their systems while exploring renewable energy and energy efficiency concepts.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
