          "_name": "content4",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content4\" group=\"Content\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video'&&bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"10\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"title col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title with Solid Background</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle align-center mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>The Energy Revolution System</b> is built around advanced electromagnetic principles, Tesla-inspired engineering concepts, and modern energy optimization techniques. At its core is a specialized energy blueprint designed to help users explore alternative power generation through magnetic field interaction, resonance tuning, and efficient energy management.<div><br></div><div>According to the <b>Energy Revolution System guide</b>, the technology utilizes carefully designed bifilar coil structures and resonance-based configurations that work together to improve energy transfer efficiency. By optimizing electromagnetic activity within the system, users can create a more stable and controlled energy environment for practical applications.</div><div><br></div><div>Each component within the <b>Energy Revolution System</b> is designed to support smooth energy flow. The blueprint explains how coil geometry, magnetic alignment, and power conditioning elements work together to enhance system performance while minimizing unnecessary energy loss.</div><div><br></div><div>One of the key concepts behind the <b>Energy Revolution System</b> is resonance optimization. Proper frequency tuning helps improve electrical stability, supports efficient power transfer, and contributes to long-term operational reliability. Combined with capacitive energy management and voltage regulation, the system is designed to maintain consistent performance.</div><div><br></div><div>Another important feature of the <b>Energy Revolution System</b> is its modular architecture. Users can start with a basic setup and expand their energy system over time by adding compatible modules, battery storage solutions, and power management components. This flexibility makes it suitable for a variety of energy learning projects and alternative power applications.</div><div><br></div><div><b>The Energy Revolution System</b> also emphasizes safety and efficiency. Detailed instructions cover grounding, insulation, circuit protection, and system calibration to help users better understand energy management principles while supporting stable operation.</div><div><br></div><div>Created for individuals interested in <b>renewable energy</b>, <b>energy independence</b>, and Tesla-inspired technology, the Energy Revolution System combines proven electrical concepts with modern design strategies. Rather than relying on complex machinery, the system focuses on electromagnetic induction, resonance-based energy transfer, and scalable energy solutions.</div><div><br></div><div>With growing interest from homeowners, DIY enthusiasts, and renewable energy learners worldwide, the Energy Revolution System has become a popular educational resource for those seeking to explore alternative energy technologies and gain greater control over their personal energy future.</div></h4>\n                <div class=\"mbr-section-btn align-center\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\">LEARN MORE</a>\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-primary-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\">LIVE DEMO</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
