        {
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    Enter your subtitle here\n                </h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>How To Implement The Energy Revolution System :&nbsp;</b>The Energy Revolution System is designed to provide a practical and structured approach to exploring alternative energy technology. The step-by-step blueprint focuses on efficiency, reliability, safety, and long-term performance, making it accessible for beginners and experienced DIY enthusiasts alike.<br><br>With detailed instructions, wiring diagrams, and optimization guidelines, users can learn how to assemble, test, and fine-tune their system using commonly available tools and components. The goal is to create a stable and scalable energy platform that can support everyday power needs.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_anchor": "content5-22",
          "_cid": "uOMlCM3Q4B",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".counter-container": {
              "ol": {
                "margin-bottom": "0",
                "li": {
                  "margin-bottom": "1rem"
                },
                "& when (@stylizedCounters)": {
                  "counter-reset": "myCounter",
                  "li": {
                    "list-style": "none",
                    "padding-left": "1rem",
                    "position": "relative",
                    "&:before": {
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "left": "-40px",
                      "margin-top": "5px",
                      "counter-increment": "myCounter",
                      "content": "counter(myCounter)",
                      "line-height": "40px",
                      "transition": "all .2s",
                      "color": "contrast(@iconColor)",
                      "background": "@iconColor",
                      "width": "40px",
                      "height": "40px",
                      "border-radius": "50%",
                      "display": "flex",
                      "align-items": "center",
                      "justify-content": "center",
                      "& when (@squareCounters)": {
                        "border-radius": "0"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "_name": "content9",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content9\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Stylized Counters\" name=\"stylizedCounters\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Square Counters\" name=\"squareCounters\" condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#1f6463\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"counter-container col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">While the claims made by the Quantum Millionaire program may seem incredible at first glance, a closer examination reveals the potential underlying truths. The program's foundation lies in the understanding that our perception of life often shapes our reality. By shifting from self-limiting beliefs such as \"I am always going to stay broke\" or \"nothing good ever comes to me,\" Quantum Millionaire encourages individuals to alter their narratives. The \"Two Cups Quantum Leap\" method proposes that one's aura and energy can attract and retain positive circumstances.\n<div>\n</div><div>Here are some of the remarkable benefits this manifestation method asserts:</div></h4>\n                <div class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                    <ol>\n                        <li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Precision Coil Construction : </b>Learn the correct winding techniques, spacing methods, and layering patterns that help improve magnetic interaction and support efficient energy flow.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Advanced Magnetic Integration :</b>&nbsp;Proper magnetic alignment helps maximize induction performance while reducing unnecessary energy loss throughout the system.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Energy Storage Setup :</b>&nbsp;Connect power conditioning components, battery storage, and inverter systems to create a smooth and reliable energy management process.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Built-In Protection Measures :</b>&nbsp;Follow practical guidelines for grounding, insulation, and circuit protection to support safe and dependable operation.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Flexible Power Expansion :</b>&nbsp;Start with a compact setup and increase capacity over time by adding compatible modules as energy requirements grow.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Smart Energy Recovery :</b>&nbsp;Optimize energy utilization through advanced feedback concepts designed to improve consistency and system balance.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Resonance Enhancement :</b>&nbsp;Match electrical components correctly to support stable energy transfer and improved operational efficiency.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Heat Reduction Design</b>&nbsp;<b>:</b>&nbsp;Utilize airflow and cooling principles that help maintain reliable performance during extended operating periods.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Intelligent Power Distribution : </b>Manage energy usage efficiently through monitoring tools, smart controllers, and automatic load-balancing solutions.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Performance Optimization : </b>Use testing and calibration procedures to evaluate voltage, current, and overall system effectiveness for long-term reliability.</span></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li>\n</li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li>\n                    </ol>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
